  "blurb": "A magnificent beachfront villa set directly on the sand at Plai Laem — six en-suite bedrooms across 750 m² on a 1,850 m² freehold plot, a 15.5-metre infinity-edge pool over the ocean, a children's pool and a rooftop terrace, minutes from Choeng Mon and under ten from the airport.",
  "detail": "This magnificent six-bedroom beachfront villa is one of Koh Samui's most exclusive properties — set directly on the sand in the serene Plai Laem area for a rare combination of privacy, space and uninterrupted ocean views. Spanning 1,850 m² of freehold Chanote land with roughly 750 m² of built area, it suits both family life and entertaining, as a private residence or a prestige investment.\n\nSix spacious en-suite bedrooms, a maid's room, a fully fitted modern kitchen and generous indoor-outdoor living open to an expansive beachfront terrace, where floor-to-ceiling windows frame panoramic sea views and ocean breezes flow through the home. A rooftop terrace and multiple lounge zones extend the entertaining space across the multi-level plan.\n\nThe centrepiece is a 4.6 × 15.5-metre infinity-edge pool overlooking the ocean, with a separate 3 × 7-metre children's pool for younger guests, backed by both private-well and government water for reliability. Plai Laem keeps Choeng Mon Beach, Fisherman's Village and the island's premier dining minutes away, with Samui International Airport under ten minutes — a turnkey, move-in-ready beachfront asset in one of Samui's strongest locations.",
